-- U.S. RESEARCH ROUNDUP-New Residential Investment, Xoma, Yelp 
-- 
-- Fri Oct 10, 2014 04:51AM EDT
-- None



Oct 10 (Reuters) - Wall Street securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several U.S.-listed companies, including New Residential Investment and Xoma, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS * New Residential Investment <NRZ.N>: Piper Jaffray starts with neutral; target $6.50  * Xoma Corp <XOMA.O>: Roth assumes coverage with buy  * Yelp Inc <YELP.N>: Sterne Agee starts with buy; price target $85Following is a summary of research actions on U.S. companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.   * Biodelivery Sciences International Inc <BDSI.O>: Roth cuts to neutral from buy  * Carefusion Corp <CFN.N>: Leerink raises target to $58 from $46; rating market perform  * Endo International Plc <ENDP.O>: Leerink raises target to $88 from $84; rating outperform  * Family Dollar Stores INC <FDO.N>: Jefferies raises target to $85 from $79; rating buy  * Juniper Networks Inc <JNPR.N>: JP Morgan cuts target to $22.50 from $30; rating overweight * Juniper Networks Inc <JNPR.N>: Suntrust cuts price target to $28 from $30; rating buy  * Manitowoc Company Inc <MTW.N>: Jefferies cuts price target to $23 from $25; rating hold  * Microchip Technology Inc <MCHP.O>: Credit Suisse cuts target to $45 from $50; outperform  * New Residential Investment <NRZ.N>: Piper Jaffray starts with neutral; price target $6.50  * Pennymac Financial Services Inc <PFSI.N>: Piper Jaffray starts with overweight; target $18 * Pennymac Mortgage Investment Trust <PMT.N>: Piper Jaffray starts with neutral; target $23  * Wayfair Inc <W.N>: Wedbush starts with outperform; price target $40 * Xoma Corp <XOMA.O>: Roth assumes coverage with buy  * Xoma Corp <XOMA.O>: Roth assumes coverage with price target $9